          <En>A formal or official prohibition of something</En>
          <Example>The government issued a ban on single-use plastics to reduce pollution.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="38a23bfe-193d-40fa-a2cd-83e5011633d8">
